WEBVTT

04:37.069 --> 04:38.404
Yes, Dad?

04:38.445 --> 04:39.738
Come here, son.

04:46.203 --> 04:47.371
What is it?

04:49.373 --> 04:51.125
I have some news for you.

04:53.877 --> 04:55.754
Your sisters are coming home.

04:57.006 --> 04:59.299
But your mother is not.

05:01.010 --> 05:02.011
What do you mean?

05:04.972 --> 05:08.934
Your mother decided to leave us.

05:08.976 --> 05:11.770
She went to live with the enemy.

05:11.812 --> 05:17.234
Allah punished her for this.

05:20.070 --> 05:21.572
The enemy...

05:23.032 --> 05:25.284
killed your mother.

05:30.456 --> 05:33.042
May God have mercy on her.

05:46.055 --> 05:49.058
We're going to take revenge.

05:49.099 --> 05:52.352
They're going to pay
a high price.

05:52.394 --> 05:55.981
A very high price.

10:25.417 --> 10:26.501
My Sheikh.

19:25.415 --> 19:27.333
There it is.

19:28.835 --> 19:29.961
Slowly, slowly.

20:18.551 --> 20:20.094
No, no, no... Look!!

20:22.889 --> 20:23.890
Let's leave it!

20:23.932 --> 20:25.767
The seven remaining are enough.

21:14.315 --> 21:16.234
Wrap it...

21:16.275 --> 21:17.568
Slowly, sweetie.

25:42.750 --> 25:44.710
My brothers in God...

25:46.128 --> 25:48.089
As you know,

25:49.215 --> 25:52.134
you came to me from all over

25:52.176 --> 25:55.846
to be an example of a new order.

25:58.099 --> 26:01.811
Those of you who follow
God's will...

26:01.852 --> 26:04.063
will have

26:04.105 --> 26:06.732
for generations to come

26:06.774 --> 26:09.110
the pride and recognition

26:09.151 --> 26:13.197
that it all started with you.

26:14.115 --> 26:15.533
May peace be with you

26:15.574 --> 26:17.660
in the name of
God most merciful.

26:17.702 --> 26:18.661
Praise God!

26:18.703 --> 26:19.954
God is great!

26:19.996 --> 26:21.580
-Praise God!
-God is great!

39:08.722 --> 39:09.848
Did you get everything?

39:09.890 --> 39:11.349
Yes, I did.

39:18.482 --> 39:19.941
Give this to him...

39:19.983 --> 39:21.610
and tell him we are grateful.

39:35.499 --> 39:36.416
Thank you.

39:36.458 --> 39:37.876
No problem.

39:53.016 --> 39:55.268
Let's go.
